column2: SELECT TOP #  spp.mjd,spp.plate,spp.fiberid, spp.SPECTYPEHAMMER, spp.SPECTYPESUBCLASS,spp.TEFFADOP,spp.LOGGADOP,spp.FEHADOP,spp.SNR, spp.SPECOBJID, p.survey, p.programName, p.instrument FROM sppParams AS spp JOIN PlateX as p on p.plateID=spp.PLATEID WHERE  spp.TEFFADOP > # AND spp.LOGGADOP > # AND spp.FEHADOP > # AND spp.SNR > #
